reviewText: One movie listed on the box was missing
Wonderful old movies from a bygone era of movie making. Garbo is great in that she had a subtle style of acting that is timeless. The movies themselves are interesting.
It is good but didn't realize that the titles and descriptions were in Korean.  At least we were able to watch movies in English.
Very nice item, even better than pictured.

They say her beauty and style captivated men and women alike...This is not as good as the production by TNT hosted by Glenn Close in the early '90s, but its a close second as far as a bio-doc.
